{
  "stem": "19242.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he's not a relative.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He just another-- he lived in the same town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was no relative of mine or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then by the end of the war, I think, I got-- I got hit with the shrapnel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I couldn't-- I was no use to them no more, for I mean, basically, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You didn't-- I couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had to be incapacitated in the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How did you get hit?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were shooting of us because we're running away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they hit me right in the-- hit me right here and knocked out a couple ribs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it must be the Germans because we run away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went after one mission and it was unsuccessful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they chase you all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They chase them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I'm the only guy got hit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the other one run away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The mission was we want to get-- get rid of a couple of Germans and take their guns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it didn't work, and it backfired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a vehicle.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- and see, I can't remember even that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is-- this is next to Miedzyrzecz and them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a forest, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Poland, there was a lot of big forest with wood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I couldn't even remember that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought we were going where we could have more guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could operate a better, a more efficient, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was not, maybe 10 guns and 100 and some people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was not enough guns.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, I mean, a lot of-- and then-- and then the war, I notice it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And people got malnutrition and they got sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
